Weight: 0.1 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HIE, HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/enchanter/armour/neck.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/neck.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/neck.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/neck.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
